document_title: Author Correction: Multi-omics analysis of multiple missions to space reveal a theme of lipid dysregulation in mouse liver
summary_full: This document is an author correction for a previously published article in Scientific Reports (10.1038/s41598-019-55869-2). The correction addresses inaccuracies in the affiliations of two authors, Hossein Fazelinia and Deanne Taylor. The original affiliations were incorrect, and the document provides their updated and correct affiliations. No changes are made to the scientific content of the original article.
conclusions: The authors have corrected errors in the listed affiliations for Hossein Fazelinia and Deanne Taylor. The scientific findings and conclusions of the original article remain unchanged.
impact_statement: This correction ensures accurate author attribution and institutional information for a study on spaceflight-induced lipid dysregulation in mouse liver.
